<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 12:22:11 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>消息人士称，谷歌与富士康合作在印度生产 Pixel 手机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/google-ties-up-with-foxconn-make-pixel-phones-india-sources-say-2024-05-23/</link><description>两位直接知情人士周四表示，Alphabet 旗下的谷歌正计划在印度南部泰米尔纳德邦生产 Pixel 智能手机，并已与台湾富士康建立合作关系。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 12:03:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/google-ties-up-with-foxconn-make-pixel-phones-india-sources-say-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>大型投资者向新兴市场注入资金，掩盖了新兴市场的资金外流</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/bigger-investors-pouring-money-into-emerging-markets-belie-em-outflows-2024-05-23/</link><description>美国银行一位资深经济学家告诉路透社，大资金投资者开始在新兴市场投入更多现金，因为他们追逐回报，这可能是他们配置资金方式的结构性转变。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 11:54:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/bigger-investors-pouring-money-into-emerging-markets-belie-em-outflows-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲汽车制造商需要时间而不是关税来抵御中国竞争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/european-automakers-need-time-not-tariffs-fend-off-china-competition-2024-05-23/</link><description>行业高管在路透社的一次活动中表示，欧洲汽车巨头不会有太多时间重组其业务和产品线以与崛起的中国汽车制造商竞争，而且更严格的关税对维持现状无济于事。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 10:44:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/european-automakers-need-time-not-tariffs-fend-off-china-competition-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>起亚摆脱电动汽车需求放缓的影响推出紧凑型电动SUV</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/kia-shrugs-off-slowing-ev-demand-launch-compact-electric-suv-2024-05-23/</link><description>起亚公司周四推出了该公司首款基于其专用电动汽车平台打造的紧凑型电动运动型多用途车，并相信即使全球电动汽车市场势头停滞，它也能通过有竞争力的价格赢得买家。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 10:07:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/kia-shrugs-off-slowing-ev-demand-launch-compact-electric-suv-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：英伟达在美联储、台湾和英国民意调查紧张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-05-23/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 10:03:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>由于手机销量强劲，第一季度超出预期，小米将电动汽车目标提高至 12 万辆</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/xiaomi-reports-27-rise-q1-revenue-strong-smartphone-sales-2024-05-23/</link><description>中国小米表示，今年的目标是交付 12 万辆电动汽车 (EV)，高于最初的 10 万辆目标，并将实施双班制生产，以满足日益增长的电动汽车需求。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 09:52:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/xiaomi-reports-27-rise-q1-revenue-strong-smartphone-sales-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>监管机构表示，中国推动公司股息应该吸引投资</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-push-company-dividends-should-attract-investment-says-regulator-2024-05-23/</link><description>中国一位高级监管机构周四表示，鼓励企业支付更多股息的政府政策应该会让中国股市对海外投资者更具吸引力。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 09:34:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-push-company-dividends-should-attract-investment-says-regulator-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>泰国医院称新加坡航空航班上的20人仍在重症监护室</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thai-hospital-says-20-people-singapore-airlines-flight-remain-intensive-care-2024-05-23/</link><description>一名医院官员周四表示，周二新加坡航空一架航班遭遇严重湍流并紧急迫降曼谷，机上的 20 名乘客仍在重症监护室接受治疗。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 09:33:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thai-hospital-says-20-people-singapore-airlines-flight-remain-intensive-care-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>中国通过模拟攻击向台湾新总统发出严厉警告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/with-mock-attacks-china-sends-honed-warning-taiwans-new-president-2024-05-23/</link><description>北京发起了为期两天的惩罚演习，以抗议台湾新就任总统赖清德的分裂本能，这是发出了精心设计的警告。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 09:32:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/with-mock-attacks-china-sends-honed-warning-taiwans-new-president-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>万科获批28亿美元境内银团贷款</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-vanke-granted-28-bln-onshore-syndicated-loan-facility-2024-05-23/</link><description>现金短缺的大型房地产开发商万科周四表示，已获得 200 亿元人民币（合 27.6 亿美元）的银团贷款融资，并将继续推进其他融资以增加流动性。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 09:26:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-vanke-granted-28-bln-onshore-syndicated-loan-facility-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>大众汽车首席财务官：具体讨论印度汽车合作伙伴关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-cfo-concrete-discussions-over-car-partnerships-india-2024-05-23/</link><description>大众汽车公司财务主管周四表示，该公司正在就在印度进行乘用车生产合作进行具体谈判，并补充说，在仍然存在“明显”机会的市场上赚钱很困难。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 09:20:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-cfo-concrete-discussions-over-car-partnerships-india-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>伦敦证券交易所数据显示，印度、埃及是 4 月份俄罗斯海运燃料油和 VGO 出口的首要目的地</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/india-egypt-top-destinations-russian-seaborne-fuel-oil-vgo-exports-april-lseg-2024-05-23/</link><description>交易商称，伦敦证券交易所数据显示，印度和埃及是 4 月份俄罗斯海运燃料油和减压柴油 (VGO) 出口的首要目的地。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 09:17:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/india-egypt-top-destinations-russian-seaborne-fuel-oil-vgo-exports-april-lseg-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>耶伦希望七国集团针对中国产能过剩筑起“反对墙”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/yellen-says-g7-discuss-responses-chinas-excess-industrial-capacity-2024-05-23/</link><description>美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦周四表示，她希望市场驱动的国家就中国国家驱动的产业政策向中国筑起“反对之墙”，这是她在本周的七国集团财政会议上推动的一个关键问题。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 09:12:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/yellen-says-g7-discuss-responses-chinas-excess-industrial-capacity-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>亿滋国际因跨境贸易限制被欧盟罚款3.66亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/mondelez-fined-3657-mln-euros-by-eu-cross-border-trade-curbs-2024-05-23/</link><description>周四，奥利奥制造商亿滋国际因阻碍欧盟国家之间巧克力、饼干和咖啡产品的跨境贸易而被欧盟反垄断监管机构处以 3.375 亿欧元（3.657 亿美元）的罚款。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 09:10:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/mondelez-fined-3657-mln-euros-by-eu-cross-border-trade-curbs-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，中国国家储备库计划购买多达 15,000 吨钴</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-state-stockpiler-aims-buy-up-15000-t-cobalt-sources-say-2024-05-23/</link><description>三名知情人士告诉路透社，中国计划在未来几个月内从中国本土生产商购买最多 15,000 吨钴金属作为国内库存，并补充说这将是单次采购的创纪录数量。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 08:46:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-state-stockpiler-aims-buy-up-15000-t-cobalt-sources-say-2024-05-23/</guid></item></channel></rss>